---Dockerfile---

1. Download Anaconda 
2. Download Docker Desktop
3. Open the PowerSHell 
4. Change the directory do that all the files are in one place 
5. You can do this by: 
   mkdir C:\Users\Maria\android_world_docker
   cd C:\Users\Maria\android_world_docker
6. Create the Dockerfile and place this code: 
   FROM continuumio/anaconda3:latest
   WORKDIR /workspace
   COPY . /workspace
   RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y adb wget unzip curl
   RUN conda create -y -n android_world_env python=3.10
   RUN /bin/bash -c "source /opt/conda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate android_world_env && pip install -r requirements.txt"
   CMD ["/bin/bash"]

--Build Docker Image--
1. In the Anaconda PowerShell, run: 
   docker build -t android_world_geny_image
   docker run -it `-v "C:/Users/Maria/Genymotion/tools:/platform-tools" `--privileged `android_world_geny_image `/bin/bash
   export PATH=$PATH:/platform-tools
   chmod +x run.sh
   ./run.sh
